{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "霍普 第5话 为了保护憧憬的骑士",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "要是对方这样砍过来，\\n就这样把剑拨开……\\n在这瞬间刺过去！对，就是这样。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "霍普……\\n又在祭坛上模仿骑士吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "打扫工作呢？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "打扫工作，我已经完成了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "骑士训练，唔，\\n算是我的癖好……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "的确，一点灰尘都没有呢。\\n挺厉害的嘛。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "不过你怎么突然认真打扫了？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "啊，该怎么说，我……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "我有点，想认真地，\\n成为一名祭司了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这样啊！\\n我觉得是很不错啦……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "不过之前你不是\\n想当骑士、不想当祭司吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "怎么突然改变想法了？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "就是……之前……\\n跟魔兽对战时，我发现了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "治疗受伤的伙伴，\\n以及获得畏惧争斗的人们的信任，\\n这些事……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "都是骑士做不到，\\n只有祭司才能做到的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "我现在依旧憧憬着骑士，但是……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "正因为如此，我想成为祭司，\\n而不是骑士。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "总有一天，\\n我要成为出色的祭司……\\n守护我所憧憬的骑士。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "霍普……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "原来如此……\\n我会全力支持你追求目标！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "话虽如此……\\n如果你真心想成为祭司，\\n就要离开这座城堡了吧……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "啊，\\n关于这件事……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "可以的话，\\n我还是想留在这里。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "可是……留在这座城堡，\\n能累积当祭司的经验吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "我来到这座城堡后……\\n感觉自己作为一名祭司，成长了很多。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "毕竟，\\n我作为见习祭司旅行期间，\\n一点都不想当祭司……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "在城堡住了一段时间后，\\n却开始认真地\\n想成为祭司了呢！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "所以我认为……\\n想累积当祭司的经验，\\n留在城堡，是最好的选择。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "而且，大家常常\\n在战场上受伤不是吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "要累积治愈魔法的经验，\\n也没有比这里\\n更适合的地方了吧……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "所以说……\\n王子，拜托了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "请让我继续在这里修行吧！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "当然可以。\\n往后也请多关照，霍普。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "有你在，\\n我也能安心作战。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "今后就拜托了，霍普。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "嘿嘿……埃尔菲莉丝前辈。\\n尤蒂尔王子，\\n我会继续努力！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "一定会用这根法杖，\\n守护两位……不，\\n守护这座城堡的所有人！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}